        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You were a research scientist working at Fermi labs, an attractive candidate for the Embrace by the Tremere clan. They hoped your logical mind and sound education with the scientific method would help you study Thaumaturgy. Unfortunately, they were wrong. You struggle with accepting the superntural realities of your life, as they have no scientific basis. You can't begin to understand half of why Kindred life is the way it is, much less blood sorcery. And because you cannot understand it, you are not very capable of using it. However, as thaumaturgically inept as you might be, you're more than aware of the 'publish or perish' mentality of the Pyramid. Maybe you can't understand magic, but you understand bureaucracy, and the importance of people skills. So you've turned yourself into a natural toady. Whoever's boots need licking, you'll do it. You've managed to fake your way up the Apprentice ranks, and are beginning to sweat a bit. Bootlicking will only take you so far. And while you continue to ingratiate yourself, you'd better damn well hope that some charitable Tremere will be amenable to helping you get over your mental blocks regarding magic and the supernatural."
        ],
